PROJECT DESCRIPTION
----------------
This project contains automated UI tests written in Java using:
- Selenium WebDriver
- Cucumber (BDD)
- JUnit
- Page Object Model
- WebDriverManager
- Maven

The tests are for a job offer form in a React-based application embedded in an iframe.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
- Java JDK 17+
- Maven 3.x
- Chrome browser (or other if configured)
- ChromeDriver (automatically managed by WebDriverManager)

RUNNING TESTS
----------------------
From the terminal:

Building and running:
-mvn clean test

From the IDE (e.g. IntelliJ):
- Run the `TestRunner.java` class as a JUnit test